{"tid":1901051,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己係輕度弱智","createTime":"2020-02-27T14:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T03:00:42.000Z","uid":81190,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8c78ef1ab70461cbad158c2ed99442ff219b17","tid":1901051,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"可能平時人地未必覺，但一去到做嘢嘅時候就有好多甩漏，好多好細微嘅話都做錯、甚至被人提一提先諗到點做<br />\n<br />\n中學讀書讀得好差，係得要背書嘅科先高分。<br />\n所以經濟、數學呢啲科都讀得好差<br />\n數學都係靠死操先唔洗fail<br />\n<br />\n去到番工又係咁，好多都係要要人講要人教<br />\n<br />\n所以話，一個人生得聰明真係好緊要"},{"pid":"b2857298310166ac0b8b567c2057fef9de7892e5","tid":1901051,"uid":36297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"咪成日扮弱智啦 唔教你就識就係天才"},{"pid":"919f066023704e2465d6931879e7db6ed5da29b8","tid":1901051,"uid":301552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"6e032a771e35cd156e78a9456aad87d544ffddd4","tid":1901051,"uid":81190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2857298310166ac0b8b567c2057fef9de7892e5","tid":1901051,"uid":36297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"咪成日扮弱智啦 唔教你就識就係天才"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"根本蠢人冇資格生存"},{"pid":"4bc5a684fd5dc7b045be0dbbc29c45497967a86a","tid":1901051,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"放心 好多人都係咁"},{"pid":"dc5707dbbd3105d5dce5cda079f52f430a8d8719","tid":1901051,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:59:13.000Z","msg":"你知自己弱智都未蠢得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fe66af00ce4bd43e928abe2d744eee491b940c","tid":1901051,"uid":86119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"Same 我都係一味靠背 個腦好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50854076c21122ef06873398c665419df2bb1f33","tid":1901051,"uid":9104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"以為自己出po 越大越蠢 做多錯多 做一百件事總有幾個錯 錯完又錯 集中力有問題咁撚樣 讀書反而唔差可能讀既係自己有興趣既野 但出黎做正經野就變弱知仔 一日幾小錯 十日一大鑊 <br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTeluIEfPXzGH66iunw16m_sdmbUerY5OvpeQlv1cJWj9YoHxb3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcTeluIEfPXzGH66iunw16m_sdmbUerY5OvpeQlv1cJWj9YoHxb3&h=ce5907b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a9254875bd53289e9acbb39222ee24e7f28e9a2","tid":1901051,"uid":345516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"Same<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大讀書都差過人，運動又廢，基本上無咩優點⋯⋯但係點都無諗過自己智力有問題⋯⋯今日去見工要做iq test，拎返個分果時見到有60分⋯⋯以為都幾好⋯⋯起碼合格⋯⋯點知望一望下面個表⋯⋯正常人係80-120⋯⋯當下我心諗⋯⋯唔撚係掛⋯⋯乜原來我弱智⋯⋯？<br />\n講真生存左廿幾年⋯⋯從來無諗過依件事會發生喺我身上⋯⋯好迷茫⋯⋯我依家唔敢返屋企⋯⋯唔知點面對屋企人⋯⋯原來佢地一直照顧住個弱智仔⋯⋯真係辛苦晒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6de35afaccfcb018923f5c0e7942f77e9c3212","tid":1901051,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"我公司一半人以上都係咁，好正常"},{"pid":"e4a4a18155ca7f231e43bbdf0d857ac494eb7772","tid":1901051,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"每日錯一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec8229c93377e0ed28aacb9392f69c0ac3b2277","tid":1901051,"uid":3028,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T15:28:44.000Z","msg":"冷靜D照下鏡, 睇下自己個樣, 同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦<br />\n<br />\n世界好公平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果人人都心想事成<br />\n<br />\n會天下大亂<br />\n<br />\n世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},{"pid":"1d54394a1b24936e44d9f046c1c18586684a789e","tid":1901051,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a9254875bd53289e9acbb39222ee24e7f28e9a2","tid":1901051,"uid":345516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB